        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://exploresouthernhistory.com/sneads.html"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The 1883 arrival of the railroad turned Sneads into a key shipping hub for cotton and lumber.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        9
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://exploresouthernhistory.com/sneads.html"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Sneads was officially incorporated on October 26, 1894, and today ranks as the county’s fourth largest municipality.",
