      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sneads%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "In 1823, an African‑American trader known as the “Black Factor” or “Mulatto King” was granted a small reservation in Sneads after Florida’s transfer from Spain.",
